xpsvn-light
============

What is xpsvn-light?
---------------------
xpsvn-light (or xpsvn on command line) is a fork of xpsvn (full, non-light)
that changes the mode of operation in a way that you do not have to check
out the full SVN repository including trunk/, tags/ and branches/, but only
the files in trunk/

Status
-------
The status of xpsvn-light is currently BETA.
